   403→Helper record to derive JSON schema attributes from OWL restrictions:
   404→
   405→```java
   406→public record SchemaAttributes(boolean isArray, boolean isRequired) {
   407→    
   408→    /**
   409→     * Creates SchemaAttributes from typed RestrictionInfo list.
   410→     * Uses helper methods to determine array and required status.
   411→     */
   412→    public static SchemaAttributes fromRestrictions(YamlConfig config, List<RestrictionInfo> restrictions) {
   413→        if (restrictions == null || restrictions.isEmpty()) {
   414→            return new SchemaAttributes(false, false);
   415→        }
   416→        boolean isArray = restrictions.stream().anyMatch(RestrictionInfo::impliesArray);
   417→        boolean isRequired = config.isEnforceRequiredness() &&
   418→            restrictions.stream().anyMatch(RestrictionInfo::impliesRequired);
   419→        return new SchemaAttributes(isArray, isRequired);
   420→    }
   421→}
   422→```
