   695→- ✅ **Proper OWL semantics** - `someValuesFrom` now correctly implies required=true and minItems=1
   696→- ✅ **Centralized logic** - OWL→OpenAPI mapping in one place (`applyToArraySchema()`)
   697→- ✅ **No parsing errors** - No string-to-int conversions that could fail
   698→
   699→### Developer Experience
   700→
   701→- ✅ **IDE support** - Autocomplete, find usages, refactoring all work
   702→- ✅ **Exhaustive checking** - Sealed interface ensures all cases handled
   703→- ✅ **Self-documenting** - Types express intent better than strings
   704→
   705→## Future Enhancements (Optional)
   706→
   707→### Cleanup (Low Priority)
   708→
   709→The following fields in `SchemaVisitor` are still used but could potentially be eliminated in a
   710→future refactoring:
   711→
   712→```java
   713→// These are still actively used by ResourceSchemaMapper for range information
   714→public List<OWLObjectProperty> propertiesFromObjectRestrictions;
   715→public Multimap<String, String> propertiesFromObjectRestrictions_ranges;
   716→public List<OWLDataProperty> propertiesFromDataRestrictions;
   717→public Multimap<String, String> propertiesFromDataRestrictions_ranges;
