   759→- **Java Pattern Matching**: https://openjdk.org/jeps/441
   760→- **Sealed Classes**: https://openjdk.org/jeps/409
   761→
   762→## Conclusion
   763→
   764→The type-safe OWL restrictions refactoring successfully eliminated magic strings from the ASG
   765→codebase while maintaining 100% backward compatibility. All integration tests pass, confirming that
   766→the refactoring preserved correct behavior while significantly improving code quality,
