### Phase 4: Create SchemaAttributes Helper ✅

**Created:** `src/main/java/com/grl/component/asg/SchemaAttributes.java`

Helper record to derive JSON schema attributes from OWL restrictions:

```java
public record SchemaAttributes(boolean isArray, boolean isRequired) {

    /**
     * Creates SchemaAttributes from typed RestrictionInfo list.
     * Uses helper methods to determine array and required status.
     */
    public static SchemaAttributes fromRestrictions(YamlConfig config, List<RestrictionInfo> restrictions) {
        if (restrictions == null || restrictions.isEmpty()) {
            return new SchemaAttributes(false, false);
        }
        boolean isArray = restrictions.stream().anyMatch(RestrictionInfo::impliesArray);
        boolean isRequired = config.isEnforceRequiredness() &&
            restrictions.stream().anyMatch(RestrictionInfo::impliesRequired);
        return new SchemaAttributes(isArray, isRequired);
    }
}
```

### Phase 5: Update ObjectPropertyMapper ✅

**Modified:** `src/main/java/com/grl/component/asg/ObjectPropertyMapper.java`

Changed constructor to accept `List<RestrictionInfo>` and use `applyToArraySchema()`:

```java
class ObjectPropertyMapper {
    private final List<RestrictionInfo> restrictions;

    public ObjectPropertyMapper(MappingContext context, String name, String label, String description,
                              Boolean isFunctional, List<RestrictionInfo> restrictions, List<String> ref,
