### Phase 7: Update DataPropertyMapper ✅

**Modified:** `src/main/java/com/grl/component/asg/DataPropertyMapper.java`

Most complex mapper - uses pattern matching for boolean combinations and enum handling:

```java
class DataPropertyMapper {

  private final Set<RestrictionInfo> restrictions;

  public DataPropertyMapper(String name, String label, String description,
      @Nullable Object exampleValue,
      Boolean isFunctional, List<RestrictionInfo> restrictions,
      List<String> valuesFromDataRestrictions_ranges, List<String> type,
      Boolean array, Boolean isRequired) {
    // ... field assignments
    this.restrictions = Set.copyOf(restrictions);
  }

  private ArraySchema composedSchema() {
    ArraySchema array = new ArraySchema();
    ComposedSchema composedSchema = new ComposedSchema();

    // NEW: Pattern matching for boolean combinations
    for (RestrictionInfo restriction : this.restrictions) {
      for (String item : this.type) {
        Schema<?> schema = createSchemaForType(item);
        isRequired |= restriction.impliesRequired();
        switch (restriction) {
          case UnionOf _union -> composedSchema.addAnyOfItem(withExample(schema));
          case IntersectionOf _intersection -> composedSchema.addAllOfItem(withExample(schema));
          default -> throw new IllegalStateException("Unexpected value: " + restriction);
        }
      }
    }
    array.setItems(composedSchema);
    return array;
  }

  private void applySchemaRestrictions(Schema<?> base) {
    if (base.getType().equals("array")) {
      if (base instanceof ArraySchema arraySchema) {
        for (RestrictionInfo restriction : this.restrictions) {
          restriction.applyToArraySchema(arraySchema);
        }
      }
    } else {
      // NEW: Pattern matching for non-array restrictions
      for (RestrictionInfo restriction : this.restrictions) {
        isRequired |= restriction.impliesRequired();
        switch (restriction) {
          case DataHasValue data -> base.setDefault(data.expression().getFiller().getLiteral());
          case DataOneOf _dataOneOf -> {
            if (CollectionUtils.isNotEmpty(this.valuesFromDataRestrictions_ranges)) {
              if (base instanceof StringSchema stringSchema) {
                this.valuesFromDataRestrictions_ranges.stream().sorted()
                    .forEach(stringSchema::addEnumItemObject);
              }
            }
          }
          default -> {
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Results

